data.description: **MUST SEE THIS BEAUTIFUL 4 BEDROOM ~ 2 BATH ~ 3 CAR GARAGE HOME IN PRESTIGIOUS STERLING HILLS COMMUNITY** This spacious home has 2,384 sq ft of living area, a Tri-Split Plan Design & Vaulted Ceilings. Island Kitchen has Breakfast Bar, & includes all newer Appliances + newer Laminate Flooring + newer Ceramic Tile Flooring in Kitchen & both Bathrooms. Inside Laundry room has laundry tub & newer Washer & Dryer. The Master Bath includes Dual Sinks, separate Shower & Jetted Tub. Vivint Security System including 4 Cameras (monitoring fee $49.00 monthly). Newer Landscaping & the Gazebo conveys with home. Sterling Hills Gated Community is Deed Restricted with annual fee of $125.00 per year, includes many amenities, Pool, Tennis Court, Billiard room, Exercise room, Club House & much more. Just a few minutes to the Suncoast Parkway making an easy commute to Tampa.
